{"type": "article", "id": 35252, "title": "有了这套“皇帝的新鼓”，随时随地都能练习了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-05T23:27:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 15968, "name": "ZENLET"}, {"id": 25316, "name": "Esrawe"}, {"id": 35522, "name": "Verreum"}, {"id": 29485, "name": "Alain Gilles"}, {"id": 35523, "name": "Ignacio Cadena"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161205213655LfK4WYS1vAFVRBJT.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>ELVIS by Sushant Vohra</h3><p>在不少设计师们努力将操控灯具的方式变得远程、数码化的同时，也有人尝试着转变开关与人的互动方式。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43482557/Elvis-Ambient-Light\" rel=\"nofollow\">ELVIS</a> 是由印度设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sushantvohra\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sushant Vohra</a> 带来的一款气氛灯，造型相当简洁，仅由两片弯曲的面板构成，本身就是灯具的开关。使用时只需滑动上方的面板即可，明暗则根据滑动所形成空隙所决定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120521385036F1TsZOq2V8yGiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213851YpRm2whMS9teZTEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213850WMuz1Zr3jiFG7EKO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213850hgRY0rTad1vU4OIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213851Z4vJCj5eTRHm8Knr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chubby by Alain Gilles</h3><p>将布料和玻璃组合在一起的尝试似乎多了起来，我们之前就曾介绍过<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32518.html\">有织物压痕的吹制玻璃</a>，最近比利时设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alaingilles.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alain Gilles</a> 则为捷克玻璃制造商 <a href=\"http://www.verreum.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Verreum</a> 设计了一款将两种材料融合在一起的凳子 Chubby。凳子的底座采用了人工吹制的玻璃，富有金属光泽的表面则得益于捷克传统的镀银处理，顶部配有柔软的坐垫，抵消了玻璃带来的冰冷感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213826pMqS1B6liCaYHbtu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213826AX5vFtTnVlY7ZWfb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612052138277aUPyRMpYqxNiO98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213826bXBd7QipoN4O2UMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612052138274Ryk62x0XbOZFDGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Freedrum</h3><p>由于大件乐器对空间的要求，很难在其他地方尽情练习。瑞典设计师 August Bering 为了让十岁大的儿子能够不受限地学鼓，带领设计团队和设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.blockzero.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Block Zero</a> 联手研发了一款名为 Freedrum 的鼓棒配件。Freedrum 由黑色的长条形感应器和配套的应用组成，感应器既可以绑在鼓棒上，也可以绑在鞋子上。只要和安装了应用的设备通过蓝牙完成配对，Freedrum 会根据你所在的环境建立虚拟的位置，同时识别你敲打或是踩踏的动作，将它们转化为实际练鼓的声音。有了这么一套“皇帝的新鼓”，在没有鼓的情况下也能尽情练习了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedrum/freedrum-the-drumkit-that-fits-in-your-pocket\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 89 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213812UpmBaFWQnsCMTiOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213812wn1ztmPgV6IH3oFR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213812etLV9aZuwQz3RBjG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.872059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LIFT by ZENLET</h3><p>为了 MacBook，你额外购入了多少配置？来自台湾的设计团队 ZENLET 有感于单个配件功能的局限性，耗时近一年研发了专为 MacBook 设计的多功能框架 LIFT。像是画框一样的 LIFT 既是可以随身携带的电脑包，又可以转变成一个实用的散热支架。它采用了双框设计，铝合金外框和抗冲击的聚碳酸酯内框能够让机器不受磨损。简约轻巧的外型加上可以订制的外壳，既注重功能又提供了展现个性的时尚感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1562350776/lift-and-go-beyond-carrying-your-macbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价从 79 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213752JxAEd0WGQ6RkmlVy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213753zbqoZ3im1VugYGnO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120521375212BZcuytfkK3MQH6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213752CkBZRU6Meru9F7pz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213753kGtEyLxc3QmaI19A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Felcana</h3><p>Felcana 是一个来自英国伦敦的初创公司，专门开发针对宠物的智能设备，希望借此帮助主人和兽医们更好地理解宠物的需要。公司的第一款产品是同名的智能家居套装，由穿戴在宠物身上的项圈、放在家中各处的信标和一台枢纽设备构成。将项圈为宠物戴上后，它会配合信标更加完整地记录宠物在家中的行为和健康状态，并实时在配套的应用上显示各项数据。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/felcana/felcana-smart-sensors-to-listen-to-your-pet\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 59 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213726jB2Me3UJSyvGPIqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.394118\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213727sJaVrWjyZQxte1Ch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213728lFdTPOpHL1XG3K5B.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213729kxQ0G5lsHR87KaAb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Xinú by Ignacio Cadena &amp; Esrawe</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>这些看上去像是沙漏的容器是墨西哥设计师 <a href=\"http://www.cadena-asociados.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ignacio Cadena</a> 和设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.esrawe.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Esrawe</a> 为 Xinú 的香水联手设计的香水瓶，在确定造型的过程中他们参考了大量自然当中的几何图案以及一些抽象的前殖民时期雕塑作品。底部是一个线条优雅的吹制玻璃，上方覆盖了手工打造的木质盖子，材质间鲜明的对比加上形状上的平衡传递出一股回归自然的纯朴质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213710ksucvIVgBamnlrZE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213711tbTA9zUwJm0IjVOo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213711K3abViAro58CjLT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161205213711hcbD69nGS2WutwPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}